[B][SIZE="4"][center][img]https://i.postimg.cc/W4KQv2CV/banner-v2-6-for-thread.png[/img]
Welcome to CesiumOS, Yet another AOSP project. But this is one that will be a very different and exciting project. What differentiates us from the rest, you ask? Well that's why you're here - to find out.
[i][b]*Note[/b] This thread is optimised for both Light and Dark XDA themes. View this thread in a browser to have a magical experience![/i]:D

[img]https://i.postimg.cc/Pf6Mv2VK/Cesium-Text-Banner-About-Us.png[/img]
CesiumOS is a project that is designed to be exciting. It is something that was born out of a sea of similar-looking AOSP roms. We offer a unique, yet familiar experience for your phone. We cherry-pick features that we think will [b]*actually*[/b] be useful in your daily lives, and nothing more. Since this is the beginning of something beautiful and exciting, we will continue to add more features in the future releases. We will strive to keep the ROM bloat-free, yet still have enough features that will keep you satisfied.

[img]https://i.postimg.cc/fWxJ6Lmd/Cesium-Text-Banner-Features.png[/img]

[HIDE]
[code]
[b]STATUSBAR:[/b]
- Statusbar icons
- DT2S on status bar
- QS Header data usage 
- Network Meter customization

[b]LOCKSCREEN:[/b]
- Fingerprint authentication vibration
- DT2S of lockscreen 
- Lockscreen shortcut customization 
- Pocket mode support
- Media art

[b]NAVIGATION & BUTTONS:[/b]
- Invert navbar
- Navbar layout
- Power menu customization 
- Playback control
- Screenoff torch 

[b]UI TUNER:[/b]
- Brighness slider customizations 
- R style notification 
- Configurable custom QS header images
- Some important tweaks related to QS pannel ;)

[b]NOTFICATIONS:[/b]
- Ambient light 
- Hide smart replies
- Battery light customization

[b]BATTERY:[/b]
- Aggersive mode 
- Smart Pixels

[b]EXTRAS:[/b]
- Three finger swipe to screenshot
- Incall vibrations 
- Built in AppLock
- Extended QS Tiles for Wifi, Bluetooth, NFC, Mobile data
- Signature spoofing
- DiracFX/MiSoundFX support
- Face Unlock
- Data switch tiles 
- Call recording 
- Full screen gestures
- A lot more ;)
[/code]
[/HIDE]

[img]https://i.postimg.cc/x8y8Hxn5/Cesium-Text-Banner-Downloads.png[/img]
[url=https://sourceforge.net/projects/cesiumos-org/]Download ROM here.[/url]

[img]https://i.postimg.cc/xT5q14sT/Cesium-Text-Banner-Installation.png[/img]
[code]Clean Flash.[/code]
1. Take a backup of your phone
2. Boot to TWRP and wipe - System, Data, Vendor and Dalvik Cache
3. Flash ROM 
4. Reboot system, Setup your device
5. Flash Gapps & Magisk(optional) after first boot.

[code]Dirty Flash[/code]
1. Download Latest build
2. Boot to TWRP and Flash build
3. Wipe Dalvik Cache
4. Reboot System

